title: White Castle
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Long established American food and burger chain restaurant. Here you will find a Dr. Praeger's brand veggie burger. Vegans should specify (no mayonaise, etc). Most sauces contain dairy, so ask. Not much else for veg food in this region.
